Membership Benefits
As a member Walk for Free at Dunedin Golf Club!
You’ll have the advantage of walking where the great ones walked. Follow in the footsteps of Ben Hogan, Bobby Jones, Babe Zaharias, and others. Dunedin golf course is walking friendly. Due to the layout of our historic championship course, you won’t have to worry about hikes from the green to the next tee. Along with walking for FREE members receive all of the below benefits.
Unlimited Greens Fees (Golf Cart is Extra)
Unlimited Range Balls (Range Closes at 4 pm on Monday and 6 pm Tuesday – Sunday)
Unlimited Use of the Practice Area
10 Days in Advance Tee Time Reservations
Member Tournaments / Events
Discounted GHIN Registration
Free Dunedin Bag Tags
Member Charging Privileges for Pro Shop purchases only
Golf Bag and Push Cart Storage Available
Lockers are available for only $5 per month
Cart Plan Available
BLOCK GROUPS – If you join one of our block groups, you won’t need to make a tee time for continued play in that group. See the calendar page for available groups.

Wait List Form
At this time, we are not accepting new applications as we are at capacity. We have a Wait List for Membership. To get on the wait list, please go to the Pro Shop to fill out the necessary form, pay the $100.00 fee, which goes toward your initiation fee. Should you have any questions, please contact Cyndi Lane, Administrative Coordinator at 727-250-1054.
